Spring Break has been extended for 2 weeks

Starting Monday, March 16, 2020, the Student Centers Building Hours will be 6:30am – 10:30pm DAILY for Student Center East (SCE) and will be  6:30am – 9:00pm and CLOSED on weekends for Student Center West (SCW)
Spring Break Hours will remain in effect until Sunday, March 29, 2020.
